text: One of the better roast meat rice around the industrial area. Definitely worth traveling out here to try. Parking can be a pain though so need to take this into consideration.  And the boss is friendly and polite.
the stall is super duper clean！and the service is excellent! I live in east coast, and i’ll definitely travel all the way down here for this yummy duck rice next time!
Affordable! Delicious! The best roast duck
